Are you a fully fledged Bogan? Can you even Boge it out? Are you ready to find out the ancient Bogan secrets? If you are, then this map is just the thing for you! Bael Zharon consumes all...

This map includes the following:

  • Fleshed out buildings with multiple entry points
  • 64 player spawn
  • Breakable environment
  • Breakable lights (shoot the lights out to your advantage)
  • Secrets/Easter-eggs
